<DIV2 N="2" TYPE="homily">
<HEAD>II. HIC DICENDUM EST DE QUADRAGESIMA.</HEAD>
<P><I>Ecce nunc tempus acceptabile ecce nunc dies salutis et cetera.</I> Gode men nu beo&eth; icumen &thorn;a bicumeliche da&yogh;es and &thorn;a halie da&yogh;es uppen us &yogh;if we wullet us seolue &thorn;et is &thorn;et we ma&yogh;en on &thorn;isse gastliche da&yogh;en ibeten ure sunne &thorn;et we abbet idon er&thorn;isse &thorn;urh &thorn;e licome lust &thorn;as da&yogh;es beo&eth; iset us to muchele helpe, and to frefre al moncun, al swa moyses &thorn;e hehte heom feste &thorn;es da&yogh;es uppon &thorn;e munte of synai &thorn;et he nefre ne ete mennisses metes for drihtenes luue and ec crist hit walde habben idon. Efter &thorn;an drihten him bi-tahte twa stanene tables breode on hwulche godalmihti heofde iwriten &thorn;a ten la&yogh;e &thorn;e &thorn;a israelisce folc sceolde halden &thorn;a he heom ledde of egipte londe &thorn;er weren in &thorn;er o&eth;res tables sunderliche .iii. ibode &thorn;a weren. <I>Audi Israel. Dominus deus tuus unus est. Secundum. Non habebis nomen dei tui in uanum. Tercium. Obserua diem sab|bati</I>. &thorn;et is on englis Ihere&eth; &yogh;e israelisce bem<NOTE PLACE="marg">? bern.</NOTE> &thorn;et nis buten an god on heofene and on eor&eth;an and over alle &thorn;ing hine &yogh;e scule wur&thorn;ian and hersumen and luuian mid al euwer heorte. &THORN;e o&eth;er heste wes. Ne haue &thorn;u &thorn;ines drihtenes nome in nane a&eth;a ne in <MILESTONE N="3b" UNIT="folio">nane idel speche. in nane idel &yogh;elwunge<NOTE PLACE="marg">? &YOGH;elpunge.</NOTE>. And &thorn;e &thorn;ridde godes heste wes iwriten inne &thorn;a table. Wite &yogh;e &thorn;et &yogh;e &yogh;emen &thorn;enne halie sunnedei. and &thorn;et &yogh;e hine wur&eth;ien and halden from uwilche swinke. Nu godemen nu weren &thorn;as &thorn;reo la&yogh;e &yogh;e-writen inne &thorn;a o&eth;re<NOTE PLACE="marg">? ore <I>for</I> are.</NOTE> table breode sunderlipes alswa crist hit hefde idon 
