t cwe&eth; ure lauerd to moyses. Gif &yogh;e cherrat from me ower heortam<NOTE PLACE="marg">sic.</NOTE> and to-breca&eth; mine lare and mine la&yogh;e and mine heste for&yogh;eme&eth; o&eth;er for-ho&yogh;iet &thorn;enne scal eou sone &yogh;e waxen muchele wrake and sake here and hunger and &thorn;et eower heorte er&yogh;ian swi&eth;e and eower feond stron&yogh;ian and westmes &thorn;or&eth; uuele wederas oft and ilome scal for-wur&eth;an. stala and steorfa. swi&eth;e eow<NOTE PLACE="marg">MS. cow.</NOTE> scal hene and &yogh;e beo&eth; iseald<NOTE PLACE="marg">MS. iscald.</NOTE> eower feonde to prisune. Swa &thorn;et heo eow tintra&yogh;ed and heow iswenchet. lond heo eou aweste&eth; and eower burh heo for-berna&eth; and ehee<NOTE PLACE="marg">? ehte.</NOTE> heo aspilla&eth; and eard heo amerrad and &thorn;enne eower sunne forwor&eth;on and eou seolfan al fordon. &thorn;enne wille &yogh;e hit bireusian and sunne bimenen and to boto<NOTE PLACE="marg">? bote.</NOTE> gan. and iswica &thorn;enne &thorn;e or&eth; &thorn;a iswingla &yogh;e me &thorn;enne clepia&eth; and helpes me bidda&eth; and &thorn;et unriht for-leta&eth; and to rihte ibu&yogh;a&eth; and ic 
<PB REF="00000079.tif" N="15"> wulle eow ireden and milcian and eower lond ic wulle fri&thorn;ian and eow selfe me&yogh;han and bi-<MILESTONE N="4b" UNIT="folio"> werian. and blisse and lisse ic sende uppon monnen &thorn;e me luuie&eth; and irihte ihera&eth; &thorn;is beo&eth; godes word &thorn;e god seolf idihte. and moises bi-tahte. Al hit mei us rede and to lare &yogh;if we wulle&eth;. So&eth;liche me &thorn;unched gode men &thorn;et al &thorn;as wrake is icumen ouer alle &thorn;eode. &yogh;e hit ma&yogh;en witen iwis &thorn;et hit is al for ure sunne. hwulc mon is &thorn;et nauet to broken elche dei &thorn;as godes la&yogh;e &thorn;e ic eou nu cwe&eth;. &THORN;as la&yogh;en weren from Moyses. a &thorn;et drihten com on &thorn;is middilert for us to alesnesse of deofles onwalde and seod&eth;an he com on &thorn;isse mid|delert; he sette his mildheortnesse la&yogh;e ouer us. and ouer al moncun. &thorn;et wes &thorn;a&yogh;h we suneghie nu on &thorn;isse liue ne scal us na mon uuelien &thorn;er uore. Gif we nulle&eth; gan to bote and iswican hit is riht &thorn;et me us nede and isegge &thorn;et sceamie. Nawiht &thorn;on monne ah &thorn;on deofle &thorn;e rixla&eth; in him. Ge herde wilche la&yogh;e weren er crist wes iboren. Monimon sei&eth; &thorn;et &thorn;a weren strotige<NOTE PLACE="marg">? stronge.</NOTE> la&yogh;e and &yogh;if &thorn;a la&yogh;e weren nu nalde na mon mis-don wi&eth; o&eth;re ne wepmon ne wifmon ne meiden. fulso&eth; hit sei&eth; moni hit for-let for drihtenes eye. and moni hit forlet for &thorn;a re&eth;a dome &thorn;e &thorn;a wes. Leofe men &thorn;et we sculden &thorn;enchen nu &yogh;ef we weren iseli. Swa heh lauerd and mihti ouer heuene. and eor&eth;e &thorn;et he walde us iseon for&eth;an hit wes &thorn;a la&yogh;e &thorn;et ilke uuel &thorn;e ic dude &thorn;e. &thorn;u scoldest don me &thorn;et wes &yogh;if &thorn;u me wundedest ic sculde wundie &thorn;e &thorn;er <MILESTONE N="5a" UNIT="folio">on-&yogh;ein. &yogh;if &thorn;u me puttest in &thorn;et e&yogh;e; ic &thorn;in alswa. dunt a-&yogh;ein dunt. Alswa of neate bute &thorn;u were Monsla&yogh;e o&eth;er &thorn;u to-breke wed durge<NOTE PLACE="marg">? burge.</NOTE>. o&eth;er for-le&yogh;en heo weren &yogh;e tintra&yogh;ed ah god haue&eth; iset his mildhert-nesse la&yogh;e on gode. Ne scalt &thorn;u &yogh;elden vuel on&yogh;ein uuel nu&eth;a. ah god almihtin &thorn;e hat don &thorn;in god on-&yogh;ein his uuel. Ne do he &thorn;e neure swa muchelne teone ne wite on &thorn;isse liue ne beo &thorn;u nefre ene wra&eth; &thorn;er fore. ah forber for drihtenes luue. Gif &thorn;u dest &thorn;in uuel on-&yogh;ein his uuel. Swa muchel &thorn;a wred&eth;a bid &thorn;e mare bi-twenen eow and eour ey&thorn;er sunega&eth; bi-foran drihten and ec leter &yogh;e beo&eth; sahte. &thorn;as ruperes and &thorn;as reueres and &thorn;as &thorn;eues &thorn;et nulle&eth; nu nefre swike heore uueles &thorn;u a&yogh;est luuan heore saule for cristes luue and heore uuel &thorn;e heo do&eth; &thorn;u a&yogh;est to hetiene and wi&eth;-stewen &yogh;if &thorn;u 
<PB REF="00000081.tif" N="17"> miht al swa hit is nu la&yogh;e a londe. &yogh;if heo nullu&eth; nefre iswiken ne gan to bote; hit is riht &thorn;et me hem spille. for&thorn;an betere hit is &thorn;et heo beon ispilled of heore licome &thorn;enne mid alle fordon to &thorn;es deofles hond. Gif &thorn;in nexta freond agult wi&eth; &thorn;e beo hit of ane &thorn;inge beo hit of o&eth;re alswa moni de&eth;; bide hine luueliche &thorn;et he &thorn;e do riht. Gif he nulle; nim tweien of &thorn;ine freond and ga &yogh;et bi-sec hine. and gif he nule &thorn;e &yogh;et; men &thorn;e to halie chirche. &thorn;et is to &thorn;an preoste and to &thorn;an folke. <MILESTONE N="5b" UNIT="folio">Gif he him nule rihtlechen for preoste na for halie chirche; hald hine &thorn;enne swilche mon &thorn;e beo bute la&yogh;e and he&eth;enne monne &yogh;e ilic. &thorn;ine frond &thorn;u luuest for &thorn;am goddede &thorn;e he &thorn;e de&eth; and he &thorn;e alswa. &thorn;et nis noht. Ah &thorn;enne were &thorn;u wel his freond toward criste; Gif &thorn;u hine ise&yogh;e &thorn;et he wulle asottie to &thorn;es deofles hond and to his werkes. &thorn;et &thorn;u hine lettest. and wi&eth;-stewest &yogh;if &thorn;u mihtest and crist hafe&eth; ihaten &thorn;et &thorn;u scalt luuan &thorn;ine feond for his luue and wi&eth;-stewen his uueles &yogh;if &thorn;u muh&yogh;e. and bide for him deihwamliche &thorn;et crist hine bringe &thorn;et he icherre from &thorn;an uuelnesse ear his ende dei. Hwet halt &thorn;e wred&eth;e seod&eth;an &thorn;us god almihtin hauet ihaten uwil[c]ne cristene mon seod&eth;an he com on &thorn;is middelerd and ec &yogh;if &thorn;u agultest. o&eth;er sunegest toward drihten &thorn;et &thorn;u scalt gan to bote and niman scrift &thorn;er of al swa &thorn;e proest &thorn;e techet. Ne do &thorn;u &thorn;in uuel on-gein uuel swa me dude hwile. Al swa ic er seide. &yogh;if eni mon touward criste isunegede on Moyses la&yogh;e. he wes ipinet ermiliche to de&eth;e and ec nes his sunne no&thorn;elesse to drihten. Ah crist &thorn;urh his muchele mildheortnesse seod&eth;an he a-steh of heuene riche. and eadmode hine seolfne &thorn;et he wes iboren of ure lefdi Zeinte Marie. and he wes seod&eth;an twa and &thorn;ritti wintra on &thorn;isse liue. and seod&eth;an &thorn;rouwede de&eth; for al moncun al for ure neode nawiht <MILESTONE N="6a" UNIT="folio">for his. and ec &yogh;ef us seod&eth;an ane muchele &yogh;ef for his muchele eadmodnesse and sette &thorn;as la&yogh;e. Gif &thorn;u agultest wi&eth; &thorn;ine efen-nexta un&eth;onkes; bet hit &thorn;in &thorn;onkes hu se &thorn;u miht wi&eth; him for-&thorn;on ic wat fulwel &thorn;et &thorn;u miht agultan wi&eth; &thorn;ine euen nexta. &THORN;a wile crist &thorn;e haue&eth; ihate &thorn;et &thorn;u beode eilcmon al swa &thorn;u waldest &thorn;et me dude &thorn;e &thorn;ines &thorn;onkes. and &thorn;a &yogh;et he &yogh;ef us ane he&yogh;e &yogh;efe. Gif we sunegie&eth; towaar&eth; him we sculen gan 
<PB REF="00000083.tif" N="19"> to bote and forleten ure misdede er ure liues ende ne scal us nan mon pinian &thorn;er for al swa me dude hwile. Ah &thorn;u scalt hit ibeten al swa &thorn;in scrifte &thorn;e techet. Nu godemon crist us &yogh;ef moni freo &yogh;eue<NOTE PLACE="marg">MS. &yogh;ene.</NOTE> seod&eth;an he com on &thorn;isse midelerd nawiht for ure ernunge bute for his muchele mildheortnesse. er we weren al for|gult in to helle &thorn;urh adam ure alde feder for-&thorn;on &thorn;e he to-brec godes bebode and al for ure neode wrecche sunfule he asteh to &thorn;isse liue. and &thorn;rouwede de&eth; for us and alesde us of helle grunde mid his derewur&eth;e flesse and mid his blode and &thorn;a &yogh;et he haue&eth; us i&yogh;arket &thorn;a ecche blisse &yogh;if we wulle&eth; hit iernien in heuene riche. Nima&eth; &yogh;eme nu leofemon hwilche &yogh;ife he us &yogh;efe&eth; &thorn;et &thorn;et ear us bohte deore. and &thorn;a &yogh;et he us astalde his mildheort|nesse la&yogh;e seod&eth;an he com a-mong us &thorn;et is &yogh;if we suneged we hit sculen beote and pinian &thorn;ene wreche licome <MILESTONE N="6b" UNIT="folio">imececheliche<NOTE PLACE="marg">? imeteliche.</NOTE> &thorn;er a-&yogh;ein. for-&thorn;on &thorn;e licome luua&eth; muchele slau&eth;e<NOTE PLACE="marg">MS. slan&eth;e.</NOTE> and muchele etinge<NOTE PLACE="marg">MS. ecinge.</NOTE> and drunkunge. and glanesse.<NOTE PLACE="marg">? galnesse.</NOTE> and prude. and ouer|modinesse and o&eth;ermonnes istreon mid woh&yogh;e for-&thorn;on &thorn;e him ne lust swinken mid rihte on &thorn;isse liue. Al &thorn;et &thorn;e licome luue&eth; &thorn;et &thorn;a saule hete&eth; and wa is hire &thorn;er fore. Nu sculle we for-lete &thorn;es licome lust for-&thorn;on. and tilian to &thorn;ere saule bihof&eth;e &thorn;a hwile we ma&yogh;en &thorn;a hwile crist us wule &yogh;efen furst on &thorn;isse liue. for|&thorn;on crist us haue&eth; i&yogh;efen muchele mare blisse and forla&yogh;e on &thorn;isse liue to bi&yogh;eten heouene riche. &thorn;enne he dude &thorn;an monne &thorn;e ic er cwe&eth; er he were iboren. for-&thorn;on monimon hit forlet &thorn;et he ne misdude wi&eth; o&eth;erne for &thorn;on eisliche dome. and for drihtenes eie and &thorn;at nusten heo nawiht swa muchel of him swa we witen. bute &thorn;et heo wisten &eth;urh &thorn;e halie witege &thorn;et he wes hali and mihti and heh ouer heouene and ouer eor&eth;a and ouer alle &thorn;ing and &thorn;et he sculde cumen to &thorn;isse middeleard for ure neode and &thorn;ah heo heolden wel his la&yogh;e &thorn;a and is heste. and bi-lefden wel on him. we wrecche sunfulle ne do we noht swa. Ah sette&eth; deihwamliche sunne uppon sunne we hine sculde luuian and hersumian and halden his heste al for ure a&yogh;ene neode. for&eth;on we habbe&eth; ihereden &thorn;urh wise witega hu he erest astalde &thorn;eos woreld. Al for ure neode. and he &thorn;reowede de&eth; for us. and uwlche dei we ihere&eth; siggen. <MILESTONE N="7a" UNIT="folio">and we hit witen to so&eth;e. and 
<PB REF="00000085.tif" N="21"> we hit iseo&eth; hwilche wunder and murh&eth;e he dude. and de&eth; deihwamliche. for-&thorn;i we scolden halden his heste us bitwenan. Muchel is &thorn;ines eor&eth;liches louerdes eie. and hunfold mare is cristes eie. for&eth;on &thorn;e eor&eth;liche lauerd ne mei don na mare bote pinen &thorn;e wrecche licome to dea&eth;e. Ah godalmihtin &thorn;e mei for|don ei&eth;er &yogh;e &thorn;ine wrecche licome and &thorn;ine saule. Swilcne lauerd we a&yogh;en to dreden. &thorn;et is godalmihtin. Nu godemen summe of us for &thorn;isse weorlde lewnesse and ec for &thorn;a licome lustfulnesse. al swa ic ear cwe&eth; we ne ma&yogh;en alre coste halden crist bibode &thorn;et us is &thorn;e mare herm. for&eth;on a &thorn;is worl&eth; win&eth; on&yogh;ein us. and we on-&yogh;ein heo mid muchele earue&eth;nesse<NOTE PLACE="marg">MS. earne&eth;|nesse.</NOTE> for-&thorn;i we sunegiet on-&yogh;ein drihtenes welle ofter &thorn;ene we scolde. ah ic eow segge to so&eth;e &thorn;es &thorn;u hefdest mare deruenesse on &thorn;isse liue of &thorn;ine licome; &thorn;es &thorn;u scoldest hersumian &thorn;e bet &thorn;ine leofe drihten and halden his bibode. Gif hit itit &thorn;et &thorn;u brekest godes heste un&thorn;onkes be<NOTE PLACE="marg">? bet.</NOTE> hit &thorn;in &thorn;onkes. &thorn;et is &thorn;et &thorn;u scalt gan to scrifte and pinian &thorn;ine licome &thorn;e hit &thorn;e make&eth; don. and scenden &thorn;ene deofel for&eth;on alre erest &thorn;u &thorn;enchest &thorn;a sunne mid &thorn;ine &thorn;onke. Ne mei &thorn;e deofle &thorn;a sunne iwiten &thorn;a &yogh;et er &thorn;u habbe heo idon mid &thorn;e licome &thorn;enne kime&eth; &thorn;e deofel &thorn;er on and wit heo. and ec he writ heo in his tables. and a he wune&eth; inne fule sunne to &thorn;es monnes ende dei. bute he hine driue a-wei. <MILESTONE N="7b" UNIT="folio">Mid sod&eth;e dedbote his sunne bi reowsumnesse. &thorn;e wrecche sunfulle ne elde nawiht &thorn;et he ne ga to bote &thorn;e wile he mei to dei he mei. tomar&yogh;an hit him is awane: Leofe bro&eth;re ne ouertrowi&yogh;e cristes milce ne his mild|heortnesse al swa monimon sei&eth; and wene&eth;. Hu mei ic efre ibete ic habbe idon swa muchele and swa monifalde ne bete ic hit nefre on mine liue. O. sei&eth; &thorn;us &thorn;e boc. wei &thorn;et he eure hit wule i&thorn;enche in his &thorn;onke. Ne beo heo nefre swa frekel. ne swa heh. ne swa muchel. ne swa e&eth;elic. &thorn;ah ure an heofde idon eower alre sunne and he walde gan to scrifte and bi-reusien ha. and forleten ha a mare. &thorn;et crist almihti nule<NOTE PLACE="marg">? wule.</NOTE> milcie for his muchele mildheortnesse bute &thorn;an ilke monne &thorn;e swa &thorn;enche&eth;. swa ic er cwe&eth;. and ouer-treowe&eth; godes milce. Gif he bid&eth;ed<NOTE PLACE="marg">? bidde&eth;.</NOTE> inna &thorn;a sunne. and in &thorn;on &thorn;onke. he is al for-loren into helle grunde. and &thorn;a monne ec &thorn;a nulle&eth; ileuen. &thorn;et he wal&eth;<NOTE PLACE="marg">? walde.</NOTE> beon iboren of 
<PB REF="00000087.tif" N="23"> ure lefdi sancte marie ne &thorn;olien de&eth; for us. and ec &thorn;a sunfulle monne &thorn;e dre&yogh;e&eth; a heore uuele werkes. and &thorn;enche&eth; her on ic wille liggen a &thorn;et ic beo ealdre o&eth;er &thorn;et ic beo sec. &thorn;enne wulle ic birewsien. and beten. for&eth;on drihten is mildheorte&eth; inoh he wule hit me for&yogh;euen. &thorn;us &thorn;e deofel wule bilesnien &thorn;e wreche. and ec we ileue&eth; to so&thorn;e alswa redliche swa adam ure eldre feder us forgulte erest in to helle. <MILESTONE N="8a" UNIT="folio">Swa ne mei nan mon seggen hu muchele mare godalmihtines milce and his mildheortnesse is &thorn;er a&yogh;ein. &thorn;on sunfulle monne he hine wile biseche mid gode heorte and mid so&thorn;e dedbote his sunne &yogh;if he wile heo &thorn;urhut forleten and nimin scrift &thorn;er-of. and beten a mare. Leofe breo&eth;re and sustre &thorn;ah we numen scrift of ane sunne o&eth;re of twa. and &thorn;e<NOTE PLACE="marg">? we.</NOTE> fulie ane nis &thorn;et icweme godalmihti. Ne &thorn;e preost &thorn;e ne mei scrife bute &thorn;u wulle heo alforleten. Hu mei &thorn;e leche &thorn;e lechnien<NOTE PLACE="marg">MS. lechi|nen.</NOTE> &thorn;a hwile &thorn;et iren sticat in &thorn;ine wunde. Nefre. Ne &thorn;u ne mi&yogh;t beon wel iscrifen god almihti to cweme. bute &thorn;u heo alle for-lete ei&eth;er &yogh;e &thorn;a ane &yogh;e &thorn;a o&eth;er. wite &thorn;e wel &thorn;et &thorn;e an sunne wule amerran al &thorn;a godnesse. and &thorn;e almesse. and &thorn;a dedbote &thorn;e &thorn;u dest of &thorn;am o&eth;er. A lutel ater bitteret muchel swete. And &thorn;ah an castel beo wel bemoned mid monne and mid wepne. and &thorn;er beo analpi holh &thorn;at an mon mei crepan in. Nis hit al unnet. hwet itacnet &thorn;e castel &thorn;e mon seolf. hwet &thorn;a men &thorn;e beo&eth; in &thorn;e castel and hin &yogh;eme&eth;. &thorn;et beo&eth; &thorn;es monnes e&yogh;an. and his fet. and his hondan. and his mu&eth;. and his nesa. and his earen. her beo&eth; &thorn;a limen &thorn;et suneGet uwilene mon. &thorn;u scodeldest<NOTE PLACE="marg">? scoldest.</NOTE> heo bi|witen al swa clenliche swa crist ha &thorn;e bitahte on &thorn;as fulhtes be&eth;e. No&thorn;eles o&eth;erhwile &thorn;u sunegest mid summe of &thorn;isse <MILESTONE N="8b" UNIT="folio">limen ofter &thorn;enne &thorn;u scoldest. hit nis nan wunder &thorn;ah mon sunegie o&eth;er hwile unwaldes. ah hit is muchele muchele<NOTE PLACE="marg">sic.</NOTE> mare wunder &yogh;if he nule nefre swiken. Al swa ic er cwe&eth; hwet tacne&eth; &thorn;a wepne &thorn;ine elmisse &thorn;e &thorn;u dest. &thorn;et is &thorn;u gast to chirche blu&thorn;eliche and fedest wreche men and herebure&yogh;est and scrudest elles al &thorn;et &thorn;u maht don to gode. and &thorn;a &yogh;et &thorn;u hersumest &thorn;ere sunne &thorn;et is &thorn;et holh &thorn;et ic er cwe&eth; hwa creope&eth; &thorn;er-in; &thorn;e awariede deofel. for&eth;on &thorn;enne &thorn;e sunne bi&eth; idon. Seod&eth;an bicumet he. and wunet &thorn;er-on abute &thorn;u hit bete. hu miht &thorn;u don &thorn;ine elmesse and 
