<PB REF="00000097.tif" N="33"> &thorn;onc. Ne &thorn;enche &yogh;e herto. Gif &thorn;u me dest woh and wit beon anes lauerdes men; ic hit mene to mine lauerde alre erest &thorn;u me scalt don riht. and seod&eth;an &thorn;e lauerde. witicrist muchele strengere dom is of godalmihtine. Gif &thorn;u wilt habben for|&yogh;efenesse of &thorn;ire misdede to drihten alre erest &thorn;u most habben mine freonseipe<NOTE PLACE="marg">? freond|scipe.</NOTE> &yogh;if &thorn;u wi&eth; me agultes. and seod&eth;an &thorn;u most bi&yogh;eten milce et &thorn;ine drihtene. Tobreoke anes eor&eth;liches monnes heste; he wile wre&eth;e wi&eth; &thorn;e. hunfald mare &thorn;u scoldest halden cristes biheste for &thorn;on he is alra kinge king &thorn;e mon &thorn;e leie .xii. mone&eth; in ane prisune nalde he &yogh;efen al &thorn;et he efre mahte bi&yogh;eten wi&eth; &thorn;et he moste .xii. beo &eth;er ut of. and &thorn;ah &thorn;u leie in ane prisune o&eth;er hwile &thorn;u hefdest cla&eth; to werien. and to etene and to drinken. &yogh;e so&eth;liche on cristes prisune nis nan of &thorn;is sere; &thorn;et is in helle. ah a &thorn;er is waning <MILESTONE N="12b" UNIT="folio">and graming. and to&thorn;en grisbating. hunger and &thorn;urst. and chele. and feonda bitinga. and neddre slittinga. wa is him &thorn;et he efre wes iboren on &thorn;is liue &thorn;e &thorn;er scal wunian. For godes luue ga&eth; to scriffte of alla eower sunne. for &thorn;ah &yogh;e gan of sunne ower sunne to bote. and &yogh;e nulle&eth; forleten hordomes. and &yogh;ifernesse and druncnesse. ne halt nawiht &thorn;at scrift. and &thorn;is beot &thorn;a twa sunne &thorn;e men fulie&eth; alra swi&eth;est. and wene&eth; &thorn;et hit ne beo na sunne bute he habbe scrift. he is forloren in to helle. Gif eani mon bi&eth; inumen in &thorn;ere sunne. So&eth;liche &thorn;us sei&eth; &thorn;e boc. hwet sei&eth; &thorn;e dusie to ufele hele wes ic iboren &yogh;if ic ne mot habben on &thorn;isse weorlde &yogh;euenesse. ah swa me