<PB REF="00000099.tif" N="35"> world. Sod&eth;liche heo us truket &thorn;enne we lest wene&eth;. wei &thorn;et eni mon scal wi&eth; o&eth;erne misdon for &thorn;isse worldes &yogh;ifsunge<NOTE PLACE="marg">? &YOGH;itsunge.</NOTE>. So&eth;liche al heo a-ga&eth;. and &thorn;a wrecche saule hit scal abuggen. Ga to &thorn;ine feder burinesse o&eth;er &thorn;er eni of &thorn;ine cunne li&eth; in. and esca hine hwet he habbe bi&yogh;eten mid his wohe domas. and mid his reuunge. mid his licome lustes. mid his o&eth;re sunne. hwile he wes her on &thorn;isse liue. So&eth;liche he walde seggen &yogh;if he mihte speken. wa is me &thorn;et ic efre dude swa muchele sunne. and heo ne &yogh;e bette. for swilche pine ic habbe &thorn;et me were leofere &thorn;enne al world &thorn;ah hit were min most ic habben an alpi &thorn;ra&yogh;e summe lisse and summe le&eth;e. and ec mostic underfon minne licome and beon on worlde a mare ic walde fein pinian and sitten on forste and on snawe up et mine chinne. and &thorn;a &yogh;et hit wal&eth;<NOTE PLACE="marg">? walde.</NOTE> me &thorn;unchen &thorn;et softeste be&eth;. and &thorn;et wunsemeste &thorn;et ic efre ibad moste ic beon of &thorn;isse earme liue. and &thorn;a&yogh;et &thorn;u maht understonden &thorn;enne &thorn;u stondest et his burienesse &thorn;et he wes prud and wlonc. swa &thorn;u ert nu. and &thorn;u forwur&eth;est. eca swa he is nu al to nohte; and &thorn;u nast neure hwenne; Leof wes he on liue and la&eth; is <MILESTONE N="13b" UNIT="folio">he nu&eth;e. and &thorn;a wrecche saule forloren; for-&thorn;i leofemen under|stondet. eouseluen &thorn;a hwile &yogh;e mahten. Nis &thorn;as weorld nawiht &yogh;e hit iseo&eth; eow seluen. Ne beo he nefre swa riche for&eth; he scal &thorn;enne is dei cume&eth;. for-&thorn;i ga&eth; blu&eth;eliche to bote of eower sunne &thorn;a hwile &yogh;e ma&yogh;en. Vfel is &thorn;et mon alde&eth; and his da&yogh;es. him at-ga&eth; and nehleche&eth; his ende dei and nule him bi&thorn;enchen &thorn;et his sunnen waxa&eth;. &thorn;at is &thorn;ere saule de&eth;; for&eth;on heo ne mei abeoren alla &thorn;a sunne &thorn;e &thorn;e mon uppon hire de&eth;. &thorn;enne heo wulle ut of &thorn;on licome. So&eth;liche &thorn;us sei&eth; &thorn;a boc &thorn;et moni &thorn;usent monne mahte libben fele &yogh;ere mare &thorn;enne he do; &yogh;if he were riht-wis and god-furht leoue men &thorn;enne &yogh;e gad to scrifte ne forlete &yogh;e for nane scame &thorn;et &yogh;e ne seggen &thorn;am preoste alle eower sunne ne beo heo nefre swa ethelic. for nis nan sunne &thorn;et he ne con o&eth;er he heo wat &eth;urh. &thorn;et he heo dude him seolf o&eth;er he heo haf&eth; i-escad o&eth;er haf&eth; ifunden on boke. Nis nan sunne &thorn;et nis iwriten on boke. for-&thorn;i betere eow is &thorn;et eow sceamie bi|foren &thorn;am preoste ane; &thorn;enne on domes-dei biforen criste. and bi-foren al heuene wara. and bi-foren al eor&eth;e wara. and bi|foren 
<PB REF="00000101.tif" N="37"> al helle wara. and &thorn;a hwe&thorn;ere &thorn;ine saule feren scal in to eche pine. Leofe men ne mei &thorn;e preost for&yogh;efen <MILESTONE N="14a" UNIT="folio">nane men his sunne ne his a&yogh;ene ah he is iset bi-twihan god almihtin. and &thorn;e for &thorn;e wissine hu &thorn;u scalt et god seolf habben &thorn;ine sunne for&yogh;euene. and he hauef&eth;<NOTE PLACE="marg">sic.</NOTE> &thorn;a ilke mahte of Sancte petre to bindene. and to unbindene. and of ure biscope &thorn;e is on sancte petres stude for&eth;on he ne mei beon on ewilche stude for-&thorn;i beo&eth; &thorn;a preostes under heom. Gif &thorn;u sunegest; he &thorn;e scal reden on godes halfe hu &thorn;u scalt habben cristes freond|scipe; So&eth;liche ne &thorn;erft &thorn;u bidden namare. Ne mei nan mon seggen hu lihtliche &thorn;u maht habben godes milce. gif &thorn;u sunegest; forlet hit a mare. and &thorn;et mid rihte scrifte. and bete a. alswa ic er cwe&eth;. &thorn;ah &thorn;u ga to bote and for-heole summe &thorn;ine sunna. nis &thorn;et nawiht to &thorn;ine bi-heof&eth;e. Ne recche&eth; crist nane leasunge. ne him nis na neo&eth;<NOTE PLACE="marg">? neod.</NOTE>. o&eth;er &thorn;u most hersumian crist. o&eth;er &thorn;am deofle. Godemen uwilc mon scal beon twi&yogh;en awesscen of his sunne enes et &thorn;am fulhtbeda<NOTE PLACE="marg">? fulhtbe&eth;a.</NOTE>. for er &thorn;onne &thorn;et child beo iful&yogh;e&eth; hit is &thorn;es deofles. o&eth;er si&eth;e &thorn;u scalt beon iwesscen et so&eth; scrifte; &thorn;enne &thorn;u forletest &thorn;ine sunne. So&eth;liche &yogh;if &thorn;u wult habben bone to drihten; &thorn;u most beon on ward &thorn;ine sunnen for &thorn;us cwe&eth; &thorn;a boc. <I>peccatores deus non audit</I>. Sunfulles monnes bone nulle <MILESTONE N="14b" UNIT="folio">god almihtin iheren bute he wulle forleten &thorn;a sunne and gan to bote leofemen &thorn;ah &yogh;e sunegien and gan to bote ne lipnie &yogh;e no al to eower festene &yogh;if &