<DIV3 TYPE="creed">
<HEAD>[&THORN;E LESSE CREDE].</HEAD>
<P>Ich bileue on god feder al-mihti. schuppare of heouene and of eor&eth;e. and on iesu crist his onlepi sune ure louerd&middot; &thorn;et was ikenned &thorn;uruh &eth;e holi goste. iboren was of &eth;e meidene marie. ipined was under ponce pilate. ineiled was o&eth;e rode. dead and iburied. he lihto<NOTE PLACE="marg">read lihte.</NOTE> in to helle. &eth;e &thorn;ridde dei he a-ros from dea&eth;e to liue. and steih in to heouene. &thorn;er he sit o godes rithond feder al-mihti. &thorn;onene he kume&eth; to demen &eth;e quike and &eth;e deade. Ibileue on <MILESTONE UNIT="Cotton MS. Nero A xiv folio" N="131b">&eth;e holi goste. and on holi chirche. imennesse of haluwen. uor&yogh;iuenesse of sunnen. uleches up ariste eche lif efter dea&eth;; amen.</P>
