<HEAD>XXVI. [INDUITE UOS ARMATURA DEI.]</HEAD>
<P>[U]r hlaford sanctes paulus &thorn;e is &thorn;eoden lareaw. us mane&eth;<MILESTONE UNIT="Cott. Vesp. A. 22. folio" N="58b"> and mene&yogh;e&eth; of sume wepne to nemene &thorn;us cwe&eth;ende. <I>Induite uos armatura dei.</I> Nan man ne nem&eth; wepne buto to fihten mide. ne nanman ne fiht buton wi&eth; his if&oacute;menn. Ute we nu isi wice bio&eth; ure if&oacute;. and wice wepne we scule nemen a&yogh;enes ham. &AElig;lc cristen m&aacute;n &aacute;non se step&eth; up of<NOTE PLACE="marg">MS. os.</NOTE> &thorn;e funte wer he ifulled his. ipicches he mace&eth; him &thorn;ri if&oacute;n. for &thorn;an &thorn;e hit is &iacute;write. <I>Nemo potest duobus dominis seruire.</I> Nan ne mai twan hlaforde &thorn;e wransehte bien s&aacute;mod &thorn;&oacute;wie. &thorn;as &thorn;ri ifon be&eth;. Se 
<PB REF="00000307.tif" N="243"> forme is se deofel. and his ig&eacute;ng. Se o&eth;er &thorn;es middennard. Se &thorn;ridde is wel nieh &thorn;e cristen men. &thorn;at is his a&yogh;on flesc. &THORN;as &thorn;ri fihte&eth; agen elcen ileafful man alse longe se we i&eth;ese westen of &thorn;esser woruld wandri&eth;. alse &thorn;ri reaferes. &THORN;er for sede se hali iob. <I>Milicia est uita hominis super terram.</I> Cnihtscipe is mannes lif upen eor&eth;e. In &thorn;es deofles heriscole fihte&eth; ag&eacute;n &uacute;s his iferred &yogh;ewerged gastes. and un&thorn;eawes. and unwraste lahtres. In &thorn;es middeneardes iscole. sel&eth;en and unisel&eth;en. In &thorn;es flesces iscole. euel &yogh;e&thorn;anc and fule lustes. Of &thorn;e formen seie&eth; sanctus paulus. <I>Non est nobis coluctatio aduersus carnem et sanguinem. et cetera.</I> Of &thorn;an o&eth;ren cwe&eth; sanctus Iohannes se godspellere. ku&umacr;<NOTE PLACE="marg">? kue&eth;inde.</NOTE>. <I>Nolite diligere mundum nec ea que in mundo sunt.</I> Of &thorn;e &thorn;ridde que&eth; sanctus paulus. <I>Caro concupiscit aduersus spiritum.</I> S[t]range bie&eth; &thorn;es if&oacute;. and swice wi&eth; wam we ne mu&yogh;e gri&eth; ne sibbe m&aacute;cie. o&eth;er hi ofer cume&eth; us o&eth;er we him. Gif hi us ofercume&eth; ne ceped hi of hus gold ne selfer bute ure bane. Gif we ofercumed heom. we scule bien &iacute;mersed alle gode cempen and imeaded mid heahere mede. Ac se &thorn;e ge&eth; into fihte wi&eth;-ute heretoche. him mai sone mislimpe. Vte we nu isi wa scel beon ur here|toche. and se&eth;e wice ure wepne bien scu[l]e. Ur heretoche is se haligost. and ure laford ihesu crist &thorn;e sei&eth;. <I>Sine me nichil potestis facere.</I> &THORN;u ahst to habben ehte wepnecin. &thorn;a beo&eth; sceold. helm and brenie. swrd and spere. Stede and twei sporen. and ane smearte &yogh;erd. Hwic scule beon ure sceld. sanctus paulus hus sei&eth;. <I>In omnibus sumentes scutum fidei. in quo possitis omnia tela nequissimi [ignea] extinguere.</I></P>
